#2. A certain examination requires students to have 80% attendance to get the eligibility to sit. Write a program to input the number of classes held and the number of classes attended by a student and dispay his/her eligibility with the percentage of attendance.noclassesheld = int(input('Enter the number of classes held: ')) #no of classes heldnoclassesattend = int(input('Enter the number of classes attend: ')) #no of classes attendpoattendance = (noclassesattend*100)/noclassesheld #percentage of attendanceif poattendance>=80:    print(f'Your eligible for sit the exam, Percentage of your attendance: ',poattendance,'% ')else:    print('Your not eligible for sit the exam!, Percentage of your attendance: ',poattendance,'%')                